","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Brian Britt","primary":true}}]}},"person_74193_translations":{"at":1773688729608,"data":{"id":74193,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Sam Lee Chan-Sam (Chinese: 李燦森) is a Hong Kong  actor born on September 27, 1975. He started his film career when he was first spotted by director Fruit Chan who cast him in the 1997 film Made in Hong Kong (香港製造). In 2002, he appeared the Japanese film Ping Pong (ピンポン) as one of the contestants. Sam Lee is best known for the role of Sha Jang in the epic 2002 television series The Monkey King: Quest for the Sutra (齊天大聖孫悟空). Outside of his film career, he is a seasonal member of a metal/hip-hop band Lazy Mutha Fucka (LMF) where he is the rapper. Sam Lee is also known as DJ Becareful.","name":"Sam Lee","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李灿森，香港电影演员。曾演出的电影包括《香港制造》、《特警新人类》、《龙咁威2003》、《狗咬狗》等。他曾是乐队LMF的成员，并曾跟Ketchup合作；现时也是唱片骑师，代号DJ Be Careful。","name":"李灿森","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李璨琛，又名李燦森，原名李瑋璁，香港電影演員。代表作品包括《香港製造》、《特警新人類》、《狗咬狗》等。並曾跟 Ketchup 合作；現時也是 DJ，代號 DJ Becareful。","name":"李燦森","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lý Xán Sâm","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сэм Ли","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sam Lee","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сем Лі","primary":false}}]}},"person_3021181_translations":{"at":1773688734375,"data":{"id":3021181,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"　　中国内陆青年演员、模特，北京乐漾影视传媒有限公司旗下艺人，曾参演《萌妃驾到》。参与爱奇艺“天鹅计划”成功入选武侠轻喜剧《恋恋江湖》。","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xu Kaixin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xu Kaixin","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сюй Кай Синь","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中國內陸青年演員、模特，北京樂漾影視傳媒有限公司旗下藝人，曾參演《萌妃駕到》。參與愛奇藝“天鵝計劃”成功入選武俠輕喜劇《戀戀江湖》。","name":"徐凱鑫","primary":false}}]}},"person_558015_translations":{"at":1773688738510,"data":{"id":558015,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Vladimir Simonov","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"Родился в городе Октябрьск, Куйбышевская область, РСФСР, СССР. Окончил Театральное училище имени Б.В. Щукина в 1980 году и был принят в МХАТ. В 1988 перешел в труппу театра имени Евгения Вахтангова. Участвовал в спектаклях Театра им. К.С.Станиславского, Театра Наций, театра \"Et cetera\". Снимается в фильмах. Работал с такими режиссерами, как М. Швейцер, А. Эфрос, П. Фоменко, И. Дыховичный. Заслуженный артист РФ (1995). Народный артист РФ (2001).","name":"Владимир Симонов","primary":true}}]}},"person_84507_translations":{"at":1773689202991,"data":{"id":84507,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kazuya Nakai (中井 和哉, born November 25, 1967) is an award-winning Japanese voice actor and narrator who was born in Kobe, Japan. From a young age, he was interested in anime. Growing up he had interests like volleyball and archery. He was working as a civil servant in a technical field at 25 when he decided that's not how he wanted to live his life, so he enrolled into a voice acting school he attended on his days off and on weekends while still working. Despite starting his career as a narrator, he took off as a voice actor and became a big name when he got the role of Roronoa Zoro, a character he definitely wanted to voice.\n\nHe narrates programs including information and news programs and voices many iconic characters such as Roronoa Zoro from One Piece, Toshiro Hijikata from Gintama, Date Masamune from Sengoku Basara, Mugen from Samurai Champloo and Jin Sakai in the Japanese dub of the video game Ghost of Tsushima.  He loves driving, practicing archery and spending time with his dog and cat.","name":"Kazuya Nakai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"나카이 카즈야","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"中井和哉","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中井和哉（日语：中井 和哉／なかい かずや Nakai Kazuya，1967年11月25日—）为日本男性声优，所属事务所为青二Production。出身于兵库县神户市，身高169cm，体重64Kg，血型A型。声线粗犷，辨识度极高。","name":"中井和哉","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中井和哉是日本的男性聲優。出身於兵庫縣神戶市，所屬公司為青二製作。","name":"中井和哉","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kazuya Nakai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kazuya Nakai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"นากาอิ คาซึยะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kazuja Nakai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kazuya Nakai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"Kazuya Nakai (中井 和哉) è un pluripremiato doppiatore e narratore giapponese nato il 25 novembre 1967 a Kobe, in Giappone. Fin da piccolo si è interessato agli anime e crescendo ha avuto interessi come la pallavolo e il tiro con l'arco. A 25 anni lavorava come funzionario pubblico in un settore tecnico quando decise che non era così che voleva vivere la sua vita, così si iscrisse a una scuola di doppiaggio che frequentava nei giorni liberi e nei fine settimana, pur continuando a lavorare.\n\nNonostante abbia iniziato la sua carriera come narratore, è decollato come doppiatore ed è diventato un nome importante quando ha ottenuto il ruolo di Roronoa Zoro, un personaggio che desiderava assolutamente doppiare. È narratore di programmi, tra cui quelli di notizie e informazione, e dà voce a molti personaggi iconici come Roronoa Zoro di \"One Piece\", Toshiro Hijikata di \"Gintama\", Date Masamune di \"Sengoku Basara\", Mugen di \"Samurai Champloo\" e Jin Sakai nel doppiaggio giapponese del videogioco \"Ghost of Tsushima\". Ama guidare, praticare il tiro con l'arco e passare il tempo con il suo cane e il suo gatto.","name":"Kazuya Nakai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PT","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kazuya Nakai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kazuya Nakai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"Кадзуя Накаї (中井 和哉, нар. 25 листопада 1967 р.) — відомий японський актор озвучування та оповідач, який народився в Кобе, Японія.\n\nЗ дитинства він цікавився аніме. У дитинстві він захоплювався волейболом і стрільбою з лука. У 25 років він працював державним службовцем у технічній сфері, коли вирішив, що так не хоче жити, тож він записався до школи озвучування, яку відвідував у вихідні та вихідні, працюючи.  Незважаючи на те, що він розпочав свою кар’єру як оповідач, він почав працювати як актор озвучування та став гучним іменем, коли отримав роль Ророноа Зоро, персонажа, якого він точно хотів озвучити. Він веде оповідання програм, включаючи інформаційні та новинні програми, і озвучує багатьох культових персонажів, таких як Ророноа Зоро з One Piece, Тошіро Хіджіката з Gintama, Дате Масамуне з Sengoku Basara, Муґен із Samurai Champloo та Джін Сакаї в японському дубляжі відеогри Ghost of Tsushima.  Він любить їздити за кермом, займатися стрільбою з лука та проводити час зі своїм собакою та котом.","name":"Кадзуя Накаї","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"中井和哉為日本男性聲優，所屬事務所為青二 Production。出身於兵庫縣神戶市。聲線粗獷，辨識度極高。","name":"中井和哉","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кадзуя Накай","primary":false}}]}},"person_1681_translations":{"at":1773689203697,"data":{"id":1681,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Tessyo Genda (玄田 哲章 Genda Tesshō, born May 20, 1948 in Okayama Prefecture) is a Japanese voice actor, affiliated with 81 Produce. When he debuted, he used his real name, Mitsuo Yokoi (横居 光雄) as an artist name.","name":"Tessyo Genda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"玄田哲章（げんだ てっしょう，Genda Tesshō），1948年5月20日出生于日本冈山县，日本男性声优、演员、解说员。\n\n以独特的粗而浑厚的低鼻音著名，常给巨汉、肌肉男、冷酷的恶役等类型角色配音。\n\n代表作有《圣斗士星矢》系列阿鲁迪巴朗、《城市猎人》系列海坊主、《变形金刚》擎天柱、《魔神英雄传》龙神丸、《百兽王》青铜强、《火影忍者》九尾、《海贼王》凯多、《蜡笔小新》动感超人等。","name":"玄田哲章","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tesshô Genda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"玄田哲章","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"겐다 텟쇼","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tessyo Genda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"玄田哲章是日本的男性聲優、演員、旁白，本名為橫居光雄。出身於岡山縣，所屬公司為 81 Produce。","name":"玄田哲章","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tessyo Genda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тэссё Гэнда","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Teššó Genda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tesshō Genda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tessyo Genda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тешшьо Ґенда","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"玄田哲章是日本的男性聲優、演員、旁白，本名為橫居光雄。出身於岡山縣，所屬公司為 81 Produce。","name":"玄田哲章","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tesshō Genda","primary":false}}]}},"person_5993167_translations":{"at":1773689204474,"dat